    "content": "This guide helps you get started with Leadhive and connect with the perfect industry expert for your needs.\n\n<Prerequisites>\nBefore you begin, make sure you have:\n\n- A clear understanding of your project needs\n- Basic information about your requirements\n- An idea of your timeline\n</Prerequisites>\n\n## 1. Share Your Needs\n\nTo find the best expert for you, we need some details:\n\n- **Service Type**: Real Estate, Landscaping, or other services\n- **Location**: Your address and postal code\n- **Timeline**: When you need the service\n- **Specific Requirements**: Any special needs or preferences\n\n<Note variant=\"info\">\n  It takes just 2 minutes to share your needs, and our service is completely free with no obligations.\n</Note>\n\n## 2. Get Expert Proposals\n\nAfter sharing your needs, you'll:\n\n1. Receive proposals from qualified professionals\n2. View detailed expert profiles\n3. Compare rates and service plans\n\n<Image\n  alt=\"Leadhive expert matching\"\n  src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/r-6-yk-gGPtjfbIST9-8uA/compare-proposals/public\"\n  width={1200}\n  height={675}\n/>\n\n## 3. Choose Your Expert\n\nTo select the best professional, consider:\n\n1. **Compare Proposals**\n   - Review service rates\n   - Evaluate proposed strategies\n   - Check past results\n   - Read client testimonials\n\n2. **Assess Expertise**\n   - Local knowledge\n   - Experience with similar projects\n   - Communication style\n   - Availability\n\n<Note variant=\"warning\">\n  Take time to review all proposals before making your decision.\n</Note>\n\n## 4. Start Your Project\n\nOnce you've chosen your expert:\n- Review and sign agreements\n- Plan project timeline\n- Discuss strategy and approach\n- Set up milestones\n\n## 5. Track Progress\n\n1. **Project Management**\n   - Regular updates\n   - Progress tracking\n   - Communication hub\n   - Performance monitoring\n\n2. **Project Completion**\n   - Quality assurance\n   - Final review\n   - Feedback collection\n   - Future planning\n\n<Image\n  alt=\"Leadhive dashboard\"\n  src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/r-6-yk-gGPtjfbIST9-8uA/dashboard-preview/public\"\n  width={1200}\n  height={600}\n/>\n\n## Managing Your Project\n\nIn your Leadhive dashboard you can:\n- Track project status\n- Communicate with experts\n- View progress updates\n- Access analytics and insights\n\n<Note variant=\"success\">\n  Our customer service team is available via chat and phone if you need help!\n</Note>\n\n## Frequently Asked Questions\n\n1. **How long does it take to receive expert proposals?**\n   - Usually 24-48 hours\n   - Faster in major areas\n   - Depends on service type\n\n2. **Is the service really free?**\n   - Yes, Leadhive is completely free for clients\n   - You only pay standard industry rates to your chosen expert\n\n3. **Can I switch experts?**\n   - Yes, if you're not satisfied we can help you find a new expert\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- [View Success Stories](/customers)\n- [Compare Experts](/)\n- [Contact Support](/contact)",
